{"tid":1373781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我係元朗人，今日對你地班入黎元朗搞事既人有話想講","createTime":"2019-07-27T16:16:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:39:58.000Z","uid":171139,"like":42,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1288cc21c489d9c81951656c58b4218859d2165c","tid":1373781,"uid":171139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:16:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">做得好！！！</span></span><br />\n無諗過會有28萬人<br />\n仲要今日我周圍問，有好多人都係來自其他地方<br />\n近有屯天，遠有將軍澳，仲有九龍、港島、離島人<br />\n無諗過咁多人入黎撐我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我曾經以住元朗為豪<br />\n因為街外人話元朗好多好野食（雖然我唔知有咩咁好食）<br />\n因為街外人話搭輕鐵個感覺好神奇（我淨係知好臭）<br />\n因為街外人話村屋又平又大風景好（其實交通好唔方便）<br />\n但呢啲街外人印象 ，令我覺得元朗係好地方<br />\n對比市區，港島係銅臭味既話，元朗就係牛屎味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n直到上星期，呢個所謂既夢終於破碎<br />\n鄉黑無差別襲擊市民，警察撒手唔理<br />\n同今日警察係民區射催淚彈，西鐵站再次襲擊平民<br />\n其實終於發現，元朗真係一個好垃圾既地方<br />\n係我一直自欺欺人，對鄉黑勾結蒙蔽不理<br />\n我對作為一個元朗人為恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但同時<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我對作為一個香港人為豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n多謝各位巴絲，山長水遠入黎元朗征戰<br />\n作為元朗地頭蛇，我唯一可以做既係搏埋條命<br />\n衝到最前為你地開路，等你地可以舒服啲<br />\n真係多謝你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽到兄弟話今日光復元朗，下次光復邊到好<br />\n我想講，元朗並無真係光復到，鄉黑勾結警察問題根深蒂固<br />\n鄉黑今日唔係淆我地，佢地只係利用警民對立關係從而避戰<br />\n我地無成功擊退鄉黑，何妖仍未被清算<br />\n<br />\n我依然會作為元朗人繼續對抗鄉黑警勾結<br />\n但如果，如果有朝一日<br />\n香港成功光復既話<br />\n就煩請你地再黎一次真正咁光復元朗吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39c94c15a2307abc8319df57b8193a2e0614a49","tid":1373781,"uid":45498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"元朗巴打留名"},{"pid":"86937b1faebd242f91b9b5d38cd6d75e54751842","tid":1373781,"uid":228532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:18:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12a3df6620f04becb51dc10bce9b83684b4748c0","tid":1373781,"uid":41460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86937b1faebd242f91b9b5d38cd6d75e54751842","tid":1373781,"uid":228532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:18:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:19:41.000Z","msg":"樓主自己都有講 似你無睇完成段野"},{"pid":"c8bce40ca59f0fe8bfd9a043df38a4399c4d2d4e","tid":1373781,"uid":171139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86937b1faebd242f91b9b5d38cd6d75e54751842","tid":1373781,"uid":228532,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:18:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:24:14.000Z","msg":"嗯你岩，元朗人依然活係鄉黑之下<br />\n今日我地根本做唔到啲咩，但元朗既問題亦唔易解決<br />\n但為左大局，我會忍辱負重，先將focus放返落政府<br />\n最多咪出入小心，但總有一日香港人會成功<br />\n<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770fd9bc1614cc57a4e1451928c04df4aaa95892","tid":1373781,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T16:32:48.000Z","msg":"勇武嘅人多咗<br />\n會愈戰愈勇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好放棄"},{"pid":"bf791f33b9b733f3cb41a2c98f12f65cdc3e1e25","tid":1373781,"uid":208412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:39:58.000Z","msg":"本身諗住入嚟block尻你個柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}